data.description: This home is East Hill living at its finest! With beautiful craftsman curb appeal that welcomes you the minute you walk up to the door, you are immediately greeted by a covered front porch that is perfect for watching the Florida sunset. Heading inside the grand entrance to the foyer you will find a dedicated office space to the right behind gorgeous double doors. This space also leads into the main living area, and has the ability to be closed off on that side for privacy with an additional set of double doors. The main living area is spacious and airy, full of natural light from the large windows, and open to the modern kitchen. Complete with granite counters, a breakfast bar, timeless tilework on the backsplash, stainless appliances, 5-burner gas range, and cabinetry that matches the crown molding, this kitchen is sure to please. Before heading upstairs, note the half bath under the staircase-- perfect for entertaining. Upstairs you will find all 3 bedrooms, including the master suite that has plenty of space for a sitting area, tons of storage, and a large attached bathroom. In the master bathroom there is a separate water closet, double vanities and a large, immaculately tiled, glass enclosed shower. In the rear of the home you will find the driveway brings you back to a 1-car garage, plus a generously sized covered back patio that has access to the main living area. This home is just minutes from the water and Downtown, across the street from a children's park and there are no restrictions on short term rentals. Schedule your showing today!
